1c2dec92-c2d1-4fb9-88d9-dd585721f7dc.1eb5b8ab-abbb-4a60-bd5d-1140e57dbb0e.description=Execute specified command script on NA server Inputs\: host - hostname of NA server port - NA API port (443) comment - Comment to add to script execution, in format of "OO PA Change Ticket \# for device " name - Name of command script to execute nowait - 1, meaning job should not wait if there is another job running on he target device phost - Target device name priority - Task priority (1) sessionid - Connection session to issue command through sync - 1, meaning call returns a response only after the job has completed variables - input parameters to be passed into script Results\: scriptOutput - Results of command script execution stackTrace - Error thrown by command script execution if any verification - Change ticket verification notes section with scriptOutput and stackTrace appended 1c2dec92-c2d1-4fb9-88d9-dd585721f7dc.2684df52-e3c6-452e-b213-f7267daf3dfe.description=
Check the current date and time, and returns a java DateAndTime formatted string of it. If locale is specified, it will return the date and time string based on the locale.Otherwise, default locale will be used.

Inputs\:
localeLang - The locale language for date and time string. For example,  en or ja.
localeCountry - The locale country for date and time string. For example, US or JP. If localeLang is not specified, this input will be ingored.

Result\:
Current date and time.

Responses\:
success - Date/time retrieved successfully.
failure - Date/time could not be retrieved.
